- It also allocates an additional scratch page (`res.acl_scratch`) for decoding across pages.

✅ This part shows proper allocation of buffers according to the requested size (`buflen`).

---

#### 2. **Server Call and Response Handling**
```c
ret = nfs4_call_sync(...);
if (ret)
    goto out_free;

if (res.acl_flags & NFS4_ACL_TRUNC) {
