The code snippet includes a **validation mechanism** that checks whether the server response exceeds the expected buffer size (`res.acl_flags & NFS4_ACL_TRUNC`). When such a situation arises, it avoids proceeding with unsafe data copying and returns an appropriate error code (`-ERANGE`). This directly aligns with the **solution behavior** required to address CVE-2018-8822.

